Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们也准备好你的生日袍和生日冠了\N{\rENG}Got your birthday cape and crown ready, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给你,穿上然后在谷仓里等着\N{\rENG}Here, put 'em on and go wait in the barn.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.46,0:03:31.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么,现在坐好\N{\rENG}Okay, now sit tight.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.41,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你会喜欢这个的\N{\rENG}You're gonna love this.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,史蒂文,我开门了!\N{\rENG}Okay, Steven, open up!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}惊-\N{\rENG}Surpri--
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔\N{\rENG}Wow.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我了个-\N{\rENG}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.48,0:03:51.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃?\N{\rENG}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯,嗯,嗯\N{\rENG}Hm, hm, hm.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,你感觉还好吗?\N{\rENG}Steven, are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.35,0:04:02.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看起来不错,史蒂文\N{\rENG}You look good, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢,石榴\N{\rENG}Thanks, Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伙计,你脖子!\N{\rENG}Dude, your neck!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.22,0:04:09.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么了?\N{\rENG}What about it?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你居然有了!\N{\rENG}You have one!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.42,0:04:16.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么...你只是突然间长起来了?\N{\rENG}So...You just grew all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我刚刚突然来了魔法蹿个而已\N{\rENG}I had a magical growth spurt just now.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.65,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}酷啊,对不对?\N{\rENG}Cool, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,没错\N{\rENG}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这非常酷!\N{\rENG}It's totally cool!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}既然如此,那么让派对嗨起来!\N{\rENG}All right, then. Let's get this party started.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.97,0:04:26.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好!\N{\rENG}Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来尝尝这个饼干猫蛋糕吧!\N{\rENG}Let's eat this cookie cake!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.80,0:04:29.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给你,史蒂文\N{\rENG}Here, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔,谢谢\N{\rENG}Wow, thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,你不用解开它\N{\rENG}Oh, you don't have to untie that.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这只是个盒子\N{\rENG}It's just a box made to look
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}长得像是我花了功夫包装一样\N{\rENG}like I spent a lot of time wrapping it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦哦哦,一件新衬衫!\N{\rENG}Ohhh, a new shirt!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.91,0:04:41.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}颜色不错嘛\N{\rENG}What a pretty color.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.08,0:04:42.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}穿上看看\N{\rENG}Try it on.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,我猜尺寸不合适,既然...\N{\rENG}Oh, I guess it doesn't fit since...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,别担心-像这样就挺好的\N{\rENG}No, don't worry -- it fits fine just like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}球来啦!\N{\rENG}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我能做到,珍珠!\N{\rENG}I got it, Pearl!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不错嘛,康妮\N{\rENG}Nice, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你打的你去捡\N{\rENG}If you hit it, you get it.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别担心,我能够到!\N{\rENG}No worries. I'll grab it!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮,让我来\N{\rENG}Connie, let me.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,很棒啊,谢谢,史蒂文\N{\rENG}Oh, cool. Thanks, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没问题,康妮\N{\rENG}No problem, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.04,Normal Dialog Text,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HD897C1&}呦,把那个羽毛球拿回来吧\N{\rENG}{\c&HD897C1&}Yo, bring back that shuttlecock!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,不!\N{\rENG}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 600,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.50,Hint,,0,0,0,,格雷格抽出的专辑封面与石榴的配音Estelle的“shine”类似，不过歌手名字改为了Stella
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这首献给生日小子,\N{\rENG}This one goes out to the birthday boy,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有他最好的朋友\N{\rENG}and his best friend.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我仍然不敢相信这么长时间来你一直比我要大\N{\rENG}I still can't believe all this time you were older than me.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你应该偶尔偷偷带我去看PG-13的电影\N{\rENG}You should sneak me into a pg-13 movie sometime.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,是啊\N{\rENG}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,我只是开个玩笑\N{\rENG}No, I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我绝对不会让你去犯法的\N{\rENG}I would never ask you to break the law.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不过有趣的是我现在要抬起头看你了\N{\rENG}It's funny that I have to look up at you now, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的有趣还是坏的?\N{\rENG}Funny good or f-funny bad?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的\N{\rENG}Funny good.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,史蒂文玩的很开心\N{\rENG}Aw, Steven's having fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们真是嗨趴能手啊\N{\rENG}We know how to throw a party.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打扰一下,康妮\N{\rENG}Excuse me for a moment, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要去...整理一下\N{\rENG}I'm gonna go... Freshen up.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.69,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}马上就来\N{\rENG}Be right back.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,天哪!\N{\rENG}Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我能在剩下的日子里一直保持如此,\N{\rENG}If I can just keep this up for the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没人就会怀疑-\N{\rENG}no one will suspect a th--
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在干嘛?\N{\rENG}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们...\N{\rENG}What are...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在做什么?\N{\rENG}you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你对你的身体做什么了?\N{\rENG}What are you doing to your body?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.57,0:06:57.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔喔喔,你白天一直在拉伸你自己吗?!\N{\rENG}Whoa, whoa, whoa, have you been stretching yourself out all day?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,我只是...伸个懒腰\N{\rENG}No, I was just... Slouching.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么要这么做?\N{\rENG}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这一点也不像你\N{\rENG}It really isn't like you.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为,爸爸,我不能永远只像个孩子\N{\rENG}Because, dad, I can't stay a kid forever.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当康妮长大并成为总统后,\N{\rENG}When Connie grows up and becomes president,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.08,0:07:10.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那会让我变成什么?第一正太吗?\N{\rENG}what is that gonna make me, first boy?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,你不能一直维持拉伸的\N{\rENG}Steven, you can't just keep stretching forever.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你坚持的时间过长,你会伤害到自己的\N{\rENG}If you hold it too long, you could really hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}算了吧,其实,我是半人\N{\rENG}Yeah, well, I'm half human,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以也许我就不是这样的\N{\rENG}so maybe it works different for me.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们只能走一步看一步,对不对\N{\rENG}We'll just have to wait and see, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文...\N{\rENG}Steven...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.51,0:07:31.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那个是...直升犬属星座\N{\rENG}That one's canis helicopterus.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,呃,直升星座?\N{\rENG}Uh, uh, helicopterus?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错,狗升机!猜到了吗?\N{\rENG}Yeah, dogcopter! Get it?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在你想一个\N{\rENG}Now you make one up.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯...好吧,呃...\N{\rENG}Mm...Okay, um...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.46,0:07:43.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那个是,呃...蛇星座\N{\rENG}That one's, uh...Snake constellation.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那还...好吧\N{\rENG}That's pretty good.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你舒服吗?\N{\rENG}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看起来你好像要吐\N{\rENG}It looks like you're gonna throw up.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,还好,一切正常\N{\rENG}Oh, yeah. E-everything's fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,那不错\N{\rENG}Okay, that's good.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你得知道,说实话,我-我之前还有点担心\N{\rENG}You know, to be honest, I-I was a little worried before.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这听起来很蠢,\N{\rENG}This might sound silly,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.01,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我很高兴我能陪你一起长大\N{\rENG}but I'm really glad that I'm going to get to grow up with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Steven?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.40,0:08:15.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,到底怎么了?发生了什么?\N{\rENG}Steven, what's going on? What happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们刚才只是在聊天,然后突然间-\N{\rENG}We were just talking, then all of a sudden --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他变回婴儿了?\N{\rENG}he turned back into a baby?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对!\N{\rENG}Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伙计,我怎么说的!\N{\rENG}Dude, I told you!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.93,0:08:36.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}将你的身体拉伸这么长时间对你没好处\N{\rENG}Stretching your body out for that long is not good for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给你啦,珍珠\N{\rENG}Here you go, Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,不,不,不要把他给我\N{\rENG}Oh, no, no, don't give him to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}把他给我吧,紫晶\N{\rENG}Hand him over, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.57,0:08:46.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}接住了\N{\rENG}Here you go.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的能力对新生儿毫无作用\N{\rENG}My power means nothing to an infant.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,这个归我管吧\N{\rENG}Okay, this is my department.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你打算怎么做?\N{\rENG}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别担心,我能行的\N{\rENG}Don't worry, I got this.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}宝石人们怎么会不知所措呢?\N{\rENG}How can the gems not know what to do?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你以为她们了解如何抚养一个宝宝?\N{\rENG}You think they knew the first thing about raising a baby?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其实一直都是我,但我不知道为什么\N{\rENG}That was all me, but I don't get it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}开车原来总能让他安静下来\N{\rENG}Driving always used to calm him down.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我们该怎么让他变回去?!\N{\rENG}But how do we change him back?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.26,0:09:22.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道,听着,康妮,让我带你回家吧\N{\rENG}I don't know. Look, Connie, let me take you home.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我会在这一切都解决后给你回电话的\N{\rENG}I-I'll call you when this all gets sorted out.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等,不\N{\rENG}W-wait, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要留下来\N{\rENG}I want to stay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.21,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你确定?\N{\rENG}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只想在史蒂文身边\N{\rENG}I just want to be there for Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别担心,史蒂文\N{\rENG}Don't worry, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不论你多大对我都无所谓\N{\rENG}It doesn't matter to me what age it seems like you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是想和你在一起而已\N{\rENG}I want to hang out with you no matter what.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你爸爸仍然得运营他的洗车房,\N{\rENG}Your dad still has to run his car wash,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.55,0:09:45.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而宝石人们得去做她们的事,\N{\rENG}and the gems have to do gem stuff,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么我会在他们没空时陪你的\N{\rENG}so I'll watch you when they're not around.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也可以在与珍珠完成训练后来看你的!\N{\rENG}I can come see you after I'm done training with Pearl, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那听起来有趣吧?\N{\rENG}Doesn't that sound fun?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看看啊-他总算不哭了\N{\rENG}Look at that -- he finally stopped crying.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}总之,这是个好的开始\N{\rENG}Well, that's a start.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么了,紫晶?\N{\rENG}What's up, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文宝宝该换尿布了\N{\rENG}Baby Steven needs changing.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,我的天,哦哦哦,我的天!\N{\rENG}Oh, my gosh. Ohhh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他变得更小了?史蒂文变成微观物了!\N{\rENG}Did he get even smaller? Steven's microscopic!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他变回受精卵了!\N{\rENG}He's reverted back to a zygote!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所有人!史蒂文变成-\N{\rENG}Everyone, Steven is --
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快看,现在合身了\N{\rENG}Look, it fits now.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你又变回正常了!\N{\rENG}You're back to normal!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真对不起那变成了一场灾难\N{\rENG}Sorry this was a disaster.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只想为你变得成熟一点\N{\rENG}I wanted to look older for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那无所谓\N{\rENG}That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我听到你在面包车里说的话了\N{\rENG}I heard what you said in the van.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我不能像人类一样成长的话真的没问题吗?\N{\rENG}It's really okay if I don't age like a human?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然啦!\N{\rENG}Of course it is!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就是喜欢你这样啊\N{\rENG}I like you just the way you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,好吧!\N{\rENG}Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,史蒂文,你下巴上有东西\N{\rENG}Uh, Steven, you've got something on your cheek.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.86,0:10:47.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃?\N{\rENG}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是胡子啊!\N{\rENG}Its a facial hair!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的?\N{\rENG}Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}爸爸!\N{\rENG}Dad!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是什么,史蒂文?\N{\rENG}What is it, little man?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看这个!\N{\rENG}Look at this!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的妈,你长胡子了!\N{\rENG}Holy smokes, you're growing a beard!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真的在长大!\N{\rENG}You really are getting older!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}大家快看这个!\N{\rENG}Everybody, look at this!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难以置信\N{\rENG}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}非常有趣\N{\rENG}Very impressive.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那里还会长出更多的吗?\N{\rENG}Is there more where that came from?

